.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Flower        | amaryllis | balloon-flower            |
| Hobby       | writing | chess              |
| Job         | doctor  | software-developer |
| Transport   | car     | snowmobile         |

